---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Experience from "../components/ExperienceCard.astro";
---

<Layout title="Education - Ali Mansoor">
  <main>
    <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Education & Learning</h2>
    <p class="animate-on-scroll">
      I completed my formal education in Computer Science through quality institutions in Pakistan. My academic foundation began with intermediate studies in computer science, followed by a comprehensive bachelor's degree program where I developed expertise in software engineering, data structures, algorithms, and modern application development.
    </p>
    <p class="animate-on-scroll">
      My coursework covered fundamental computer science concepts including <i>Object-Oriented Programming</i>, <i>Data Structures & Algorithms</i>, <i>Database Management Systems</i>, <i>Software Engineering</i>, <i>Web Development</i>, and <i>Mobile Application Development</i>. I have a strong foundation in mathematics including <i>Calculus</i>, <i>Discrete Mathematics</i>, and <i>Linear Algebra</i>. Beyond formal education, I continuously engage in professional development through online courses and real-world project experience to stay current with emerging technologies and industry best practices.
    </p>

    <div class="education-container">
      <Experience
        class="animate-on-scroll"
        title="Bachelor of Science in Computer Science"
        subtitle="2021 - 2025"
        description="Comprehensive bachelor's degree program in Computer Science covering software engineering, data structures, algorithms, database management systems, web development, mobile application development, and advanced computer science concepts. Strong foundation in mathematics and practical programming skills."
        image="/images/education/fast_logo.png"
      />
      <Experience
        class="animate-on-scroll"
        title="Intermediate in Computer Science"
        subtitle="2019 - 2021"
        description="Intermediate education foundation in Computer Science with coursework in programming fundamentals, computer organization, discrete mathematics, and information technology. Developed core problem-solving skills and theoretical knowledge in computer science principles."
        image="/images/education/pgc_logo.png"
      />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: var(--color);
  }
  P {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color);
  }

  .education-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .education-container .animate-on-scroll:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; }
  .education-container .animate-on-scroll:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
